December 2010

Lars Ørum Rasmussen, Esben Sigård Nielsen, Kristian Rune Larsen, 
Martin Raspaud, Anna Geidne, Adam Dybbroe.

Danish Meteorological Institute (DMI)
Swedish Meteorological and Hydrological Institute (SMHI)


